<p style=3D"line-height:100%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%"><span style=3D"color: #000000;">Today is a ve=
ry special day! On this day, 4 years ago, you became a member of The Nation=
al Society of Collegiate Scholars at&nbsp; University of Maryland.&nbsp;</s=
pan></p>
<p style=3D"line-height:100%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%"><span style=3D"color: #000000;">Qualifying fo=
r membership with NSCS means that you excelled academically. Joining NSCS m=
eans that you valued scholarship, leadership, and service. Here are some wa=
ys that you can stay involved as an NSCS Alumnus:</span></p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<ol style=3D"line-height:175%">
<li><span style=3D"color: #000000;">Please <a href=3D"https://email.nscs.or=
g/e3t/Ctc/W2+113/d107Qc04/VXk3Ty1Zypl7W9ghMZh46mrcBW4FBnYy5LYJwKN6pj1XH3lYM=
-W8wLKSR6lZ3mhW1yZH3d4xMJj8W80QsGy6_0KtJW6qljNt9d11SjW7Vdz6Q2hdJ-kW5Cc_v566=
pLG_W20lc3j12mMb0W1Bm_BS8SBDJKW2NFz--99K5GMW1Gsff25-fh6jW5V_5bZ6sJFD8W2JTWK=
