pzZ8R8nbGW3Mw3DV6pSXGHW4npNVq5yksZvW8nxWP19gDyffW96tZ565WKP6mW5PbhXc9ltx7Bf=
2WK9mP04" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"font-weight:bold; color:#000000" rel=
=3D"noopener" data-hs-link-id=3D"0" data-hs-link-id-v2=3D"pEm+wko2"><span s=
tyle=3D"color: #981b1e;">follow NSCS&nbsp;on LinkedIn</span></a> and share =
your milestone with your network!</span><br><br></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: #000000;">We also invite you to join our exclusiv=
e</span> <span style=3D"color: #981b1e;"><a href=3D"https://email.nscs.org/=
e3t/Ctc/W2+113/d107Qc04/VXk3Ty1Zypl7W9ghMZh46mrcBW4FBnYy5LYJwKN6pj1WP3lYM-W=
6N1vHY6lZ3m_W432y501zd7_GN4xM8dgZhrnHW72QLcT7dnl5yVMwMFj3CLpGZW9fkcb27mg9Xt=
