=3D"0" data-hs-link-id-v2=3D"SAAwd+il" target=3D"_blank">LinkedIn NSCS Memb=
er Community</a></span><span style=3D"color: #000000;">&nbsp;where you can =
share perspectives with current students and alumni, as well as find out ab=
out benefits and opportunities that are exclusively available to NSCS membe=
rs.</span><br><span style=3D"color: #000000;"><em data-stringify-type=3D"it=
alic"><br></em></span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: #000000;">As an anniversary gift, take an extra 1=
5% off on the <span style=3D"color: #981b1e;"><a  href=3D"https://email.nsc=
